snippet.title: Anno 1800: DLC9 The High Life - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to the High Life!

Immerse yourself in the next chapter of the Anno 1800™ Industrial Revolution with DLC #9: The High Life.
Take your city to grand new heights with modular skyscrapers, shopping arcades and the epic Skyline Tower monument!
Your skyline will never be the same!

So... What is your vision?

SHOP NOW : https://annogame.com/1800/dlc9
